[[File:Mugger chathead.png|left]]
'''Muggers''' have a [[combat level]] of 6 and can be a threat for new players.

Muggers are [[Aggressiveness|aggressive]], which means that they attack players who are two times the mugger's combat level or less. Thus, muggers are aggressive against players from level 3 through level 12.

